author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-EBC Solicitors to be authorized advisor for Igoria Trade in Bucharest's listing
text:
Sept 18 EBC Solicitors SA :
* Signs deal to provide authorized advisor services to Igoria Trade SA in process of listing of Igoria Trade's shares on AreoMarket, alternative market of the Bucharest Stock Exchange Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
